  03 Feb 2007; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> libmcs-0.2.1.ebuild:
  Marked ~hppa (bug #165161).

  03 Feb 2007; Jason Wever <weeve@gentoo.org> libmcs-0.2.1.ebuild:
  Added ~sparc keyword wrt bug #165161.

*libmcs-0.2.1 (03 Feb 2007)

  03 Feb 2007; Tony Vroon <chainsaw@gentoo.org> -libmcs-0.2.0.ebuild,
